1. *Zapamti* da se spremiš do vikenda. (Remember to get ready by the weekend.)
2. Svi smo *zapamtili* da se ne kasni. (We all remembered not to be late.)
3. Ona je *zapamtila* njegove reči. (She remembered his words.)
4. On je *zapamtio* da se vrati do večeri. (He remembered to come back by evening.)
5. Oni su *zapamtili* da se razdvoje ujutru. (They remembered to separate in the morning.)
6. Učenici su *zapamtili* kako da rade. (The students remembered how to do it.)